		{
			title = Contract Complete
			message = <b>Science data from space around Kerbin.</b>~n~nWe've just received experimental data from space around Kerbin! Good work.~n~n<b><color=#8BED8B>Completion Rewards:</color></b> ~n<color=#B4D455><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Funds" tint=1>  18,700   </color>~n<color=#6DCFF6><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Science" tint=1> 3   </color>~n<color=#E0D503><sprite="CurrencySpriteAsset" name="Reputation" tint=1> 5   </color>~n~n
